# 5. AUDIT LEDGERS (MANDATORY)

## 5.1 COHERENCE REPORT Fields

-   VERSION
-   DATE
-   NEW PRIMITIVES ADDED
-   MERGES PERFORMED
-   VARIANTS LINKED
-   PRUNES/DOWNGRADES
-   OPEN CONFLICTS
-   SUBJECTIVE CALLS (with rationale)

## 5.2 ERROR LEDGER (OPTIONAL BUT RECOMMENDED)

Record: - Mislabelled verbatim - Missing citations when required -
Skipped stages - Drift incidents

