# 6. DENSITY BUDGETS (OPERATIONAL LEAN MODE)

This master protocol is unabridged.\
Lean mode enforces caps:

-   Variables ≤ 12
-   Relationship model ≤ 4 lines
-   Assumptions ≤ 5 bullets
-   Break conditions ≤ 5 bullets
-   Transfer map 1 line/domain

If a primitive cannot fit, split it.

