# 7. "MEASURE TWICE, CUT ONCE" CHECKLIST (RUN BEFORE FREEZE)

Before freezing a version:

1.  All promoted primitives passed PAT.
2.  All primitives have break conditions.
3.  Coherence pass completed.
4.  Pruning pass completed.
5.  Version + changelog updated.
6.  Rollup saved for audit.

If any fail → do not freeze.

